Package org.anchoranalysis.plugin.image.task.bean.labeller

Class ImageAssignLabelTask<T>

Object
AnchorBean<Task<T,​S>>
Task<ProvidesStackInput,​SharedStateFilteredImageOutput<T>>
ImageAssignLabelTask<T>
Type Parameters:
T - type of init-params associated with the filter
public class ImageAssignLabelTask<T>
extends Task<ProvidesStackInput,​SharedStateFilteredImageOutput<T>>
Assigns a label to each image and optionally 1. copies each image into directory corresponding to the label (e.g. "positive", "negative) 2. creates a single CSV file where each row is an image-label correspondence
Author:
Owen Feehan
